{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":59653,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"dz大几？","timestamp":1593353852,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59654,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"铜球\n","timestamp":1593353861,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59657,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"顺其自然","timestamp":1593353872,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59659,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"大二之后班级活动沦为班委自嗨是你清普遍现象……","timestamp":1593353902,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59674,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"多来点实惠型活动自然乐意参与。比如疫情勤关注医疗啊、天气啊、食物分享，多聊多聚少卷","timestamp":1593353994,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59677,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"群p大家踊跃参加","timestamp":1593354051,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59682,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不想参加就别强求了吧，大家都难受不是吗","timestamp":1593354113,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59689,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"班级事务是否应当存在？它的存在除了满足学校的规定以外有无实际作用？如果没有，弄好它干嘛？只会折腾班级成员","timestamp":1593354278,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59702,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我当了两年班长一年支书，我的原则一贯是对同学负责而非对上级组织负责，同学有需求我们班委努力去协调和安排，上级有安排我们底线满足，二者间有冲突时也是同学优先。四年下来，最终没过的体系的认可，但大家发展得多元而快乐。未来会怎样，来日方长。","timestamp":1593354464,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59833,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 赞","timestamp":1593355688,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59875,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 我感觉有一些是很有意义的啊 不是为了走过场的很多 而且又能积累经验 又能多交朋友","timestamp":1593356368,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59876,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 大一哈哈哈","timestamp":1593356380,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59877,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 嗯?","timestamp":1593356411,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59892,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 嗯嗯 主要是我认为有一些很有意义的事情 需要大家参与的 班委规划好了 最后响应的人寥寥无几 就觉得挺迷茫的 有时候看到根本没人理我们就真的很心累 不知道咋解决","timestamp":1593356627,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59901,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 有一些上面的任务 或者是群体性的活动 即使不是出于自愿 也在责任上是大家应该平摊的锅 可是总会有人缄默 仿佛从没安装过微信 我指的是这种  不是说自愿的活动非要强求 ","timestamp":1593356804,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59941,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 我觉得有可能有意义但是大家并不感兴趣，或者是这种需求并不是很强烈。建议在最开始的时候就先询问一下同学们的意见，比如这学期的主题团日我们班委就先想了7个主题做成问卷让大家去选，最后把主题团日搞成了专业认知hhh，让大家分组去采访系里各个研究所的老师，感觉大家还挺积极的。","timestamp":1593357168,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":59970,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 感觉你们班可能是凝聚力不够吧，建议搞一些聚会啊轰趴啊先把大家的感情搞起来","timestamp":1593357557,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":60298,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"“你觉得有意义”和“我觉得有意义”是不一样的，因此我会拒绝参加所有我觉得没意义的班级活动，也许你的同学也有这样想的。","timestamp":1593362261,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":60303,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果只有“你觉得有意义”那就是彻头彻尾的班委自嗨了，不是所有人都热衷于社工或者社交的","timestamp":1593362331,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63688,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Isabella: 2333我觉得咱俩是一个系的...","timestamp":1593430995,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":65140,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":10192,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 害怕","timestamp":1593449463,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":7,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":10192,"reply":21,"tag":null,"text":"想问问有没有同学能解决一下同学们参加班级事务态度非常冷漠的状况?害有，班委设置怎样算是合理呢?(*'へ'*)真诚发问","timestamp":1593353810,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782586,"url":"","vote":{}}}